            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
