    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> cucumber discs</strong> and<strong> cucumber batons</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining cider vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and set aside until serving – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
